Package: iosender
Version: @VERSION@
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Depends: @DEPENDS@
Maintainer: ioSender <https://github.com/terjeio/ioSender>
Description: G-code sender for grblHAL and Grbl controllers
 ioSender is a desktop application for sending G-code to Grbl and grblHAL
 CNC controllers over serial or network connections.
